properties.verseOrder: v1 c1 v2 c1 v3 c1 v4 c1

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
A
The fullness of the Godhead bodily
Dwelleth in the Lord (x3)
And we are complete in Him

verse.name: c1
verse.lines:
Complete complete
complete in Him
We are complete in Him
(sisters: glory allelu)
Complete complete
complete in Him
We are complete in Him

verse.name: v4
verse.lines:
There's nothing more that I can do
Cause Jesus paid it all (x3)
And we are complete in Him

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
It's not by works of righteousness
But by His grace alone (x3)
That we are complete in Him

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
It's by His death and burial
And resurrection life (x3)
That we are complete in Him.
